{"word":"ἀνδρεία","slug":"ἀνδρεία","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n7911\" key=\"a)ndrei/a\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἀνδρεία</orth>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ἡ</gen>, <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"dialect\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ion.\">Ion.</a></gram> </gramGrp> <orth extent=\"suff\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἀνδραποδ-ηίη</orth> (<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:7:99\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">7.99</biblScope> </bibl>), generally written <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἀνδρία</orth> in the Mss., in agreement with the opinion of <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0082.tlg002:136:8\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.D.\">A.D.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Adv.\">Adv.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">136.8</biblScope></bibl>, refuted by Orusap.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg4099.tlg001:461:53\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ EM\">EM</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">461.53</biblScope> </bibl>:—<foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀνδρεία</foreign> is required by the metre in <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg003.perseus-grc1:510\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ar.\">Ar.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Nu.\">Nu.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">510</biblScope></bibl>, and <sense id=\"n7911.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">may</tr_> always stand in t